Open Source FPV Racing Frame Version 0.1
The SOURCE TWO is a collaborative open source frame project initiated
by Team BlackSheep, targeted at FPV racers. It follows the footsteps
of SOURCE ONE, a FPV freestyle frame.
The frame design is donated to the community to empower creators
and makers, and integrate best practices and current trends faster
into a continuously manufactured product. It's a cheaper alternative
to clones that can be bought with the peace of mind
that the big brands of the FPV industry stand for.
